This is very good IF you use less sugar in the topping. The first time that I made it per the recipe, it was way too sweet. I made it a second time, but I used 1/4 cup white sugar and 1/4 brown sugar in the topping and did not change the sugar that is mixed with the fruit. It is good with any berries; in fact, I have not yet used the exact combo of fruits in the recipe. I made it for the 4th of July with blueberries - 4 cups - and 2 cups of blackberries (what I had in the refrigerator), and it was wonderful! All blueberries also very good!